    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is an absolute dream\u2014it\u2019s been totally babied and is in truly stunning condition inside and out. It looks and drives like it just left the showroom! If you\u2019ve been looking for that perfect, flawless ride that\u2019s been cared for with a lot of love, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019d love for you to come by, take a look, and see for yourself how gorgeous it is. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
