      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this impeccably preserved specimen, maintained to the most exacting standards. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, boasting a flawless exterior finish and a cabin that remains in pristine showroom condition. Mechanically unrivaled and meticulously documented, it offers a rare opportunity for the sophisticated collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle of unparalleled integrity. Experience the definitive standard of automotive excellence.",
