    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. It is in such incredible shape, it basically looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014no scratches, a pristine interior, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been truly loved and kept in perfect condition, this is the one. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself, you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
