    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade E46 M3, a definitive specimen of the S54B32 high-revving inline-six. This vehicle features a meticulously maintained powertrain with a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and documented rod bearing replacement. The chassis integrity is absolute, featuring proactive subframe reinforcement to manage the torque loads of the 3.62 limited-slip differential. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission. Finished in Laguna Seca Blue, the paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior retains its factory matte finish with zero bolster wear. This is a turn-key, enthusiast-sorted icon with optimized throttle response and a perfectly balanced 50/50 weight distribution.",
